ty_day_average":71.215,"two_hundred_day_avg":87.71455,"recommendation":"none","all_time_high":114.15,"all_time_low":16.01,"long_business_summary":"Soni Medicare Limited provides super specialty and general hospital services in India. The company provides health care services, such as patient counselling, out and in patient, emergency care, intensive care unit, dialysis centers, operation theatre, health checkups, oncology, pharmacy, laboratory, physiotherapy, blood bank, radiology, and orthopedic services. It operates Soni Hospital, a super specialty, trauma, and general hospital with specialties centers; and Balaji Soni Hospital, a multi-specialty hospital with specialty centers, as well as CT & MRI and women care centers. The company also operates Soni Nursing College that offers graduate and post graduate level nursing education services; Soni Paramedical Institute that deals with pre-hospital emergency services; and Skill Oriented National Institute that offers paramedical and skill enhancement programs in Jaipur and Dausa. The company was incorporated in 1988 and is based in Jaipur, India."}}